{"tid":1901626,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海洋公園稱因應疫情   員工下月起減薪或放無薪假","createTime":"2020-02-28T02:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T08:32:47.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"26efb8eea925487516a0533a4abfec75da88c4f4","tid":1901626,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:21:45.000Z","msg":"海洋公園宣布，因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，實施節約成本緊急措施。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園向員工發信，由3月1日起，行政級人員減薪三分一、助理行政級人員每月放8天無薪假；其餘員工按職級，分別放6天或4天無薪假。信中說，措施會實施至另行通告，會在海洋公園全面開放後再審視。<br />\n<br />\n海洋公園因應疫情，上月底宣布暫停開放，直至另行通知。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511330-20200228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511330-20200228.htm&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0fpmn865KX7g3oX29oYbiiE%3D&h=f49d67e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511330-20200228.htm&h=5646a6ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511330-20200228.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fbfffb28bc1be2ed92f7f676e5809610239321bb","tid":1901626,"uid":214502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:28:02.000Z","msg":"執柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"c7f1f93d6d02b67336bd81944933c7ee90d81b35","tid":1901626,"uid":16372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:28:29.000Z","msg":"執柒佢啦"},{"pid":"47dd4aec3d43e000ba4b22ed81bf349befc8f960","tid":1901626,"uid":42487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:29:28.000Z","msg":"要求政府撥款1000億啦屌"},{"pid":"c61c50f4159860dceecdcda3aa5682202fdf00db","tid":1901626,"uid":234589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持"},{"pid":"ac9a84e665381f7e7455beaf89c6467362879abb","tid":1901626,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T02:32:34.000Z","msg":"合併到迪士